    "Figures6b and 6cfor epoch 1 and epoch 2: These figures depict the state of the data after 1 and 2 training epochs, respectively.",
    "As training progresses, data points begin to rearrange in a certain pattern, indicating that the model is learning to differentiate between various categories or features.",
    "Figure6dTensor Fusion: This figure represents the state where text, images, and audio are fused together in a multimodal learning context.",
    "Tensor fusion is commonly used to combine different types of data to extract richer features.",
    "Figure6eTucker Decomposition: This diagram showcases the tensor decomposition performed using Tucker decomposition technique."
